Prepare to take this fight to the MAX with a free title update for Capcom Fighting Collection 2 on August 7th! Enjoy new quality of life upgrades, brand-new artwork, remix tracks from CAP-JAMS, and additional content for Street Fighter Alpha 3 UPPER, including Maki, Yun, Eagle, and Ingrid! 

Capcom vs. SNK: Millennium Fight 2000 Pro
Capcom vs. SNK 2: Mark of the Millennium 2001
Capcom Fighting Evolution
Street Fighter Alpha 3 UPPER
Project Justice
Power Stone
Power Stone 2
Plasma Sword: Nightmare of Bilstein

Experience all 8 of these amazing titles with online play and rollback netcode!

description:
Fatal Fury x Street Fighter: The dream crossover!

Ken and Chun-Li from Capcom's renowned fighting game franchise Street Fighter are coming to FATAL FURY: City of the Wolves! With Fatal Fury's Terry Bogard and Mai Shiranui having already made their mark on the roster of Street Fighter 6, Ken's release today (and Chun-Li's in Winter 2025) serves as an exciting extension of this legendary crossover.
